LA MADDALENA RADIO
COASTAL WARNING NR. 305/21 AUG 16
MESSINA STRAIT ZONE
ON AUGUST 18TH 2021 FROM 08.30 GMT TO 10.00 GMT A SWIMMING
CROSSING CHALLENGE OF MESSINA STRAIT (START FROM PELORO CAPE
SICILY AND ARRIVAL TO CANNITELLO CALABRIA REGION) WILL TAKE PLACE.
UNITS IN TRANSIT MUST REDUCE SPEED AT THE MININUM PERMITTED
AND NAVIGATE AT A DISTANCE OF NOT LESS THAN 500 METERS FROM
THE BOATS IN TOW SWIMMER IDENTIFIED FROM SIGNAL OF MAN OVERBOARD .
SHIPS AND FLOATINGS IN TRANSIT BEWARE.
